title: Fireside with the Underboss - "Trump Is Gonna Know It's A Setup"
description: Have you seen Netflix's "Fear City"? In this story, Sammy explains some behind the scenes details that weren't mentioned in the docuseries. Specifically in regards to "The Concrete Club" and how the Gambinos had a hand in setting it up.
